      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a resident of West Bengal.\n1. The applicant must be unemployed.\n1. The applicant should be enrolled with the Employment Bank as a ‘job seeker’.\n1. The applicant should be class 8th pass and above.\n1. The applicant should be between 18-45 years of age on the 1st day of April of the year in which he/she is considered under the scheme.\n1. The applicant had not to availed financial assistance /loan under any state/central government sponsored Self-Employment scheme.\n1. Only one member of a family is eligible to receive assistance under the scheme.\n\n",
